Dependencies:

libpcap:
apt install libpcap-dev

zlib:
apt install zlib1g-dev

GOOGLE TEST:
cd /usr/src # folder where you want to download src files to
git clone https://github.com/google/googletest.git
mkdir build && cd build
cmake ..
make
copy lib files to /usr/local/lib
copy header files to /usr/local/include

LCOV
sudo apt install lcov

BOOST:
apt install libboost-all-dev

PCAPPLUSPLUS:
Go to https://github.com/seladb/PcapPlusPlus/releases/tag/v23.09.
Download latest release for distro + extract
Copy include files to /usr/local/include/pcapplusplus
Copy lib files to /usr/local/lib/
Copy bin files to /usr/local/bin/
